text: Falk Schwaar (born 28 April 1971) is a German skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:German male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Germany Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bautzen
